column2: select s.ra,s.dec,  s.specobjid,teffadopunc, fehadopunc, loggadopunc,elodiervfinal,  s.psfmag_u as mag_u, s.psfmag_g as mag_g, s.psfmag_r as mag_r,  s.psfmag_i as mag_i, s.psfmag_z as mag_z,  s.psfmagerr_u as err_u,  s.psfmagerr_g as err_g,  s.psfmagerr_r as err_r,  s.psfmagerr_i as err_i,  s.psfmagerr_z as err_z,  loggadop,fehadop,teffadop ,  flags_u & (x&&&)::bigint =# as flag_u,  flags_g & (x&&&)::bigint =# as flag_g,  flags_r & (x&&&)::bigint =# as flag_r,  flags_i & (x&&&)::bigint =# as flag_i,  flags_z & (x&&&)::bigint =# as flag_z   from sdssdr9.sppparams as sp, sdssdr9.specphotoall as s, sdssdr9.phototag as pp   where s.specobjid=sp.specobjid and s.scienceprimary=# and loggadop># and  pp.objid = s.objid and  elodiervfinal between # and # and   s.type=# and   teffadopunc<# and fehadopunc<# and loggadopunc<#
